Package: ICAMS
Type: Package
Title: In-depth Characterization and Analysis of Mutational Signatures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Steve Rozen, Nanhai Jiang, Arnoud Boot
Maintainer: Steve Rozen <steverozen@gmail.com>
Description: This package has functions to read in VCF files from Strelka and GATK, 
    create SNS, DNS, ID catalogs and do different types of plotting.
